So I said, do you know any prostitutes?

35:51.775 --> 35:53.317
She said, what do you mean I know any prostitutes?

35:53.337 --> 35:54.819
What do you think I am, eh?

35:54.939 --> 35:55.660
I know prostitutes?

35:55.680 --> 35:56.401
Fuck off.

